{
  "stem": "4113.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And we sat there like this almost all night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And then early in the morning they had-- they took us to a room where they had a bunch of shoes, a bunch of shirts, and we had to run very fast to grab shoes and to grab shirts, because we were naked sitting there.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Grab shoes, grab shirts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Because the uniforms we had from Krakow were taken away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And when you grabbed [INAUDIBLE] two left shoes, right shoes, [? oh, ?] you were hit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "I grabbed a nightgown.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Must have been from a victim, a nightgown.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And it had an embroidery [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "It was very long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "It came in handy, because I developed massive diarrhea, massive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And there was no paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "I have never seen a camp as clean in my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "There wasn't a shred of paper anywheres.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I kept tearing off little pieces from that nightgown and used it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My shirt then came to here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I kept using that up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this was Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Fortunately, after a few days, we were taken away and shipped to Schindler's.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we arrived there at Schindler's, which was a God-given when we saw him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We saw messiah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soon the women came, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was at Schindler's from that time when I was assigned to the glaziers until liberation, May 8.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, at Schindler's, being at the glaziers, initially our rations were very small.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had one eighth of a loaf of bread of about this size.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you ever buy Lithuanian bread here in Chicago, that about more or less the size of the loaf.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One eighth of that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I thought that that was for breakfast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I ate it the first day, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then I found out, no, that's for the whole day.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
